<br>
The guilds like Valoran, Farsight, Paralax, Novae, all see that they were once where some of us small guilds are now. They don't feel the need, now that they are big and strong, to walk all over us. They remember what it was like and due to their kindheartedness, have agreed to help the smaller guilds get to more of the high-end game content. KGC isn't about what is best for ME, it's what's best for EVERYONE. The FFA only benefits the strong and quick. If we aren't strong and quick, we are out of luck if we FFA.<br>
